Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.65,0:00:20.09,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I put together dried up words...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.92,0:00:28.83,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}but all I want to do is convey\N my simple feelings to you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.83,0:00:34.27,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The faint wind that blew from that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.27,0:00:38.40,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I threw it away in yesterday's ruins
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.42,0:00:44.55,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}So I can live today with you with a smile
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.09,0:00:52.19,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}But still, this incident will\N continue to trouble you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.57,0:00:57.08,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}That's why it must be a goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.08,0:01:04.12,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Now we just try to understand\N each other until nothing remains
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.12,0:01:11.27,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}And eventually, we will realize\N that it was everything to us
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.27,0:01:18.01,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Sadness will run down our cheeks,\N creating a river of tears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.42,0:01:28.97,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(0,1700)}Trembling thoughts will become a strong\N whirl and melt together into one
Comment: 0,0:01:29.97,0:01:30.04,OP5,,0,0,0,,OP End
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.94,0:01:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Who're you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.05,0:02:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in a bad mood right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.81,0:02:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wanna continue to fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't go easy on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.02,0:02:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You stop your babbling, weakling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.49,0:02:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, come over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna play\Ndo-re-mi-fa-so-la-ti-do on you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.84,0:02:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,while I snap your ribs!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.16,0:02:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.84,0:02:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! He got both of my legs\Nwith his string...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.07,0:02:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you--!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.11,0:03:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Humph! Let's hear a nice sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Do!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.66,0:03:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Re!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.84,0:03:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Where is he attacking from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.09,0:03:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Your bones make\Na really low sound, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.14,0:03:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hear a much sharper reverberation,\Nshall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.08,0:03:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, I 'll go for\Na mi-fa-so tri-combination.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.22,0:04:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.93,0:04:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.94,0:04:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Last!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.74,0:04:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Lions Barrage!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:29.70,Sign_1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(468,545)}An Invitation\Nfrom the Sound
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.96,0:04:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,An Invitation from the Sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.87,0:04:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm digging in!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.79,0:04:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura! Go on, eat, eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The Chinese-style barbecued pork\Nramen noodles here are fabulous!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.88,0:04:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. It's my treat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.28,0:04:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, chef?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.26,0:04:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna treat your girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.95,0:04:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're growing up, aren't you, Naruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.19,0:04:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What the heck are\Nyou talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:05:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to have an important conversation\Nwith Sakura today...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.58,0:05:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-She's not my girl\Nor anything like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.07,0:05:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.45,0:05:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Naruto. I was little spaced out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.62,0:05:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This looks delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.79,0:05:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then... Let's eat! Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Tell me about Sasuke\Nwhile we eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.36,0:05:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke told me not to tell you this,\NNaruto, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.16,0:06:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all that guy Orochimaru's fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.68,0:06:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Kakashi Sensei said it would be fine\Nand I'd like to believe that too...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.44,0:06:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But when he was battling Gaara...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.07,0:06:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Earlier today...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.63,0:06:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke was wearing the same expression\Nas the time before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.88,0:06:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Orochimaru, huh?\NI ran into him again a little while back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.79,0:06:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.60,0:06:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was searching for\NOld Lady Tsunade...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.02,0:07:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.19,0:07:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Pervy Sage and the old lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite the fact that\Nhe was fighting two of them at once,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.51,0:07:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,he was incredibly powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.92,0:07:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He's one dangerous dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.17,0:07:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.38,0:07:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll all be fine, believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.76,0:07:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke wouldn't fall to\Nthat kind of guy's enticement.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.42,0:07:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He's already a really powerful guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.24,0:07:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,so he wouldn't need to do\Nthat kind of thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.40,0:07:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I guarantee it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.61,0:07:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.96,0:08:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does Master Orochimaru\Nwant this guy anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Kimimaro would have\Nbeen much better...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.13,0:08:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you stay in\Na seedy place like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.70,0:08:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll just remain mediocre at best.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.39,0:08:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never become strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.63,0:08:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,All my barrages were solid.\NYet this guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.46,0:08:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't seem to have\Nsustained any damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.86,0:08:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If you keep on fooling around\Nplaying Ninja with your friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.96,0:08:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,you're just gonna continue to rot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.29,0:08:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do,\NMaster Orochimaru will empower you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.92,0:08:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no meaning\Nif we take you by force, he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.05,0:08:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.31,0:09:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimme a break...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.49,0:09:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Orochimaru sure sent me\Non a bothersome mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.78,0:09:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What did you decide?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.10,0:09:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Or are you not coming?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.90,0:09:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Decide already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.90,0:09:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,When a weakling like you lags,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.46,0:09:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,it makes me wanna just finish you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.87,0:09:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Try me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.00,0:09:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You... those Curse Marks...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.69,0:09:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so sure that
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.20,0:09:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,you're the only favorite\Nof Master Orochimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,One shouldn't use Curse Marks\Nthat lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.28,0:10:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Or rather... it looks like you're not\Neven able to control the Curse Marks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.91,0:10:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If they continue to be released\Nfor a long period of time,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.64,0:10:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse Marks will progressively\Neat your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.17,0:10:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like you're still at first state,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.85,0:10:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,so the speed at which they will\Neat away at you is still fairly slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.84,0:10:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But when they have entirely eaten you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.47,0:10:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you will lose yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.84,0:10:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.47,0:10:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,In exchange for having been\Nempowered by Curse Marks,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.78,0:10:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,you will be tethered\Nby Master Orochimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.12,0:10:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We no longer have anything\Nlike freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to receive something,\None must discard something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.65,0:10:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your objective?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.11,0:10:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you and your comrades\Njust going to comfort each other
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.34,0:10:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,in this lukewarm village...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.42,0:10:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,then simply forget all about...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.91,0:10:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Uchiha Itachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.83,0:10:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget your objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.25,0:10:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This kind of village does\Nnothing more than shackle you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:11:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut your stupid ties with this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.97,0:11:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do that, you'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.35,0:11:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,be able to obtain much,\Nmore fabulous power.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.52,0:11:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget your objective!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.34,0:11:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.51,0:11:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.29,0:11:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll walk you home!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.98,0:11:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.19,0:11:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, why?\NThe streets are dangerous at night!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,They're well lit, so I'll be fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.61,0:11:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.74,0:12:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.91,0:12:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But I want to go home alone tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.95,0:12:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.91,0:12:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.41,0:12:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.76,0:13:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you hanging around in a place\Nlike this in the middle of the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,One has to pass down this road\Nto leave the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.44,0:14:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Go home and sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.12,0:14:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't you tell me anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you always silent like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.13,0:14:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't tell me one single thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.69,0:14:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should I have to tell you anything?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.68,0:14:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you to keep your nose\Nout of my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.81,0:14:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop bothering me\Nover everything I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.44,0:14:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I... make you dislike me\Nall the time, don't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.15,0:14:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We just became Genin and\Nthe Three-Man Squads were assigned...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.49,0:14:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You and I were alone for\Nthe first time, here at this very spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.62,0:15:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You got mad at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.54,0:15:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,See! That guy doesn't\Nhave parents, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.96,0:15:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He's all alone and he doesn't have to deal\Nwith parents lecturing him...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.42,0:15:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why he can sometimes\Nbe selfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Solitude...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.50,0:15:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.06,0:15:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't the same as being scolded\Nby one's parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.02,0:15:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter all of a sudden....
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You... are annoying...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess...\Nthat was long ago, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.22,0:15:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But it all began that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.18,0:15:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke and me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.77,0:16:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And also Naruto and Kakashi Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.38,0:16:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The four of us went\Non various missions, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.51,0:16:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Those were tough and\Ndifficult times, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.81,0:16:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.44,0:16:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,more than anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.66,0:16:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,it was so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.46,0:17:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I know about your family, Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.26,0:17:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But revenge...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.80,0:17:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that won't bring anyone happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.26,0:17:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No one...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.97,0:17:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.81,0:17:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,nor I.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.73,0:17:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,As I expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.32,0:17:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm different from you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.99,0:17:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm walking a road that's incompatible\Nwith the rest of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.82,0:17:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The four of us worked together...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.87,0:17:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's true that there was a time\Nwhen I thought that was my road.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The four of us have worked together,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.85,0:17:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,but in the end,\NI decided on revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's been my reason for living.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.59,0:18:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't become like\Nyou and Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.39,0:18:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to isolate\Nyourself again, Sasuke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You taught me that solitude\Nis a very rough thing that time, Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.15,0:18:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I know exactly how that feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.19,0:18:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I have both family and friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you were no longer here, Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.61,0:18:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.58,0:18:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,for me it would be the same as solitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.04,0:18:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,From here again...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.88,0:18:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,we're going to start walking\Nour new paths individually.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.72,0:18:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.47,0:18:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you so very, very much, Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.31,0:18:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If you would only be with me, Sasuke,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.82,0:18:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you regret it,\Nno matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.98,0:18:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make it fun every day and\Nyou will definitely find happiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.15,0:18:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do anything for you, Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.78,0:19:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So... I'm begging you,\Nplease stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.57,0:19:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll even help you with your revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.91,0:19:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make it happen somehow,\NI promise you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.66,0:19:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So stay here... with me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.42,0:19:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If that doesn't work for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Then take me with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.31,0:19:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are... annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.23,0:19:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.82,0:19:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If you go, I'll scream and...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.78,0:19:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.25,0:19:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.10,0:20:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.49,0:20:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We were waiting for you, Master Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.41,0:20:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your intention?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.50,0:20:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It was already decided that\Nyou would be our leader
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.18,0:20:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the moment you exited the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.25,0:20:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive our rudeness\Nup to now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.30,0:20:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care about any of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.19,0:20:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.53,0:21:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the beginning!
